{"tid":2175672,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"連續兩日！美國軍機據報再闖解放軍演練區域","createTime":"2020-08-26T15:12:17.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-27T04:06:40.000Z","uid":79563,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"86259176bb7feca61f6a378e330c35543eb4a7d5","tid":2175672,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-26T15:12:17.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1546069-20200826.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1546069-20200826.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=hjP0Q4X6c9sJGZoCRXhatk2FGjryiJR74P7%2B0uEOyUg%3D&h=c01b2ee9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1546069-20200826.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=60986873\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1546069-20200826.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n解放軍正在南海進行軍事訓練，內地傳媒報道，一架美國空軍的RC-135S戰略偵察機，一度進入南海，是連續兩日有美軍戰機飛入解放軍演練範圍。<br />\n<br />\n另外，美國國防部長埃斯珀日前在報章撰文，指美國正全面加強國防實力，應對中國共產黨的軍事威脅，又敦促各國考慮削減與解放軍的聯繫。<br />\n<br />\n在北京，外交部批評埃斯珀的言論毫無根據。"},{"pid":"14a970b59c90fcbf0984b74e3d7d5e396d6dd8b2","tid":2175672,"uid":73856,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-26T15:13:58.000Z","msg":"打飛機啦淆咩"},{"pid":"3b0a6fb9d4d5baa924f203c65fa4f865d12c9767","tid":2175672,"uid":58209,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-26T15:14:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2020/02/28/37bwTq.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2020%2F02%2F28%2F37bwTq.png&h=7c1af503&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2020/02/28/37bwTq.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2020%2F02%2F28%2F37bwTq.png&h=7c1af503&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2020/02/28/37bwTq.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2020%2F02%2F28